16 Head and pronotum of 
<taxonomicName authority="Champion, 1888" authorityName="Champion" authorityYear="1888" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Charisius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Charisius salvini" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="270" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="salvini">Charisius salvini</taxonomicName>
